Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATE EE screams]\N--[PIRATES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Q yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE NN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDon't you have any honor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men are your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThere! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Anger Explosion!\NKuro vs. Luffy, How it Ends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you are after all\Nthat dancing around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been doin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NDon't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was simply a warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThe real fight begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon I will be feasting\Non your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Complimented by the sweet\Nwine of your agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NOut of the Back Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try. You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Damn you!\NGet away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, butler-man! Right now\Nyour life really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan of three years is a\Ncomplete and total failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NLet go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look! That weird kid\Ncaught Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it! If that\Ngoofy kid manages to beat him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then that means Captain Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be able to\Nslaughter us, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PEPPER] Oh no, you don't!\N--[KAYA] Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, snot-nosed brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're one\Nstep too late, Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWouldn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That branch was getting\Nin the way of my shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Get 'em you\Ncrazy, rubber guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're goin' down,\Nyou mean bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right\Nto cheer me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NEat this, hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NDo it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groaning]\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Time for the\Nexploding star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--[JANGO groaning]\N--[KAYA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KURO] You insect!\N--[LUFFY] Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--My plan will absolutely\N--Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--not be disrupted!\N--Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That crazy rubber guy\Nbeat Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] Not even the marines\Nwere a match for Kuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Man of a Thousand Plans!\NAnd this guy still beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NJust... just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time a pirate\Nshould abandon his name
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is when he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never lose to a coward\Nwho ditches his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,betrays his friends, and\Nruns from life on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Luffy... I never\Nheard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should remember my name\Nfor the rest of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause one of these days I'm\Ngonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya did good, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NI'd expect even you to collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,after what you just\Nwent through. Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, why were\Nyou so mad earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I truly hate people\Nlike them. They're so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not how\Nfriends should act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it isn't. Most\Npirates aren't the brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,honorable people you\Nalways make out them to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say Captain Kuro\Nis pretty standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI] You're unbelievable!\N--[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,think you can keep everything\Nthat just happened here secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would we want to\Nkeep all this a secret?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Why, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We put our lives on the\Nline to save the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone'll change\Ntheir opinion of you so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being Usopp the liar,\Nyou'll be Usopp the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHILDREN cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to clear up this\Nmisunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Misunderstanding...?\NI was known as the village liar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because I lied all\Nthe time, Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They were right\Nto not believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no\Npoint in scaring people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with something\Nthat's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I seriously doubt that\Nany more pirates like Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and his gang will show up.\NThere's no reason for pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack our out-of-the-way,\Nlittle village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen up! Pretend this\Nnever happened! 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all just another\None of my great, big lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I won't force you to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can do it!\NI'll do whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for the good of the\Nvillage, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too. My lips are\Ntotally sealed, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHILDREN chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya... Will you...\NWill you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something just isn't\Nright this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda throws everything\Noff if he's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LITTLE GIRL]\NMama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that screaming liar guy\Nnot coming to town today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN]\NThat lying little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think I hurt his\Nfeelings yesterday, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be up to his old\Ntricks in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN]\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs]\NThanks guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able to\Nprotect the village without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Give credit where\Ncredit's due.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd just stood\Nby and done nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have done\Nanything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my hands on this\Nsweet, sweet treasure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that happened\Nhere today helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just come to a very\Ndifficult decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] Captain Usopp! What did\Nyou want to talk to us about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] The three of\Nyou fought well against
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,those terrible\NBlack Cat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As Captain, I'm proud of you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for being so brave\Nand courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing\Ncompared to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious. You were\Nvery courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You were scared to death,\Nbut you kept your cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,worked together as a team\Nand kept Kaya safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we overcame our\Nbiggest and most important
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,battle since we formed the\NUsopp Pirates five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when you\Nthree brave soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,were only four years\Nold. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHILDREN]\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know this\Nis sudden, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided that I'm gonna\Nset out to sea by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT]\NUh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally gonna leave this\Nplace and become a real pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I wasn't sure\Nwhat I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't decide if I wanted\Nto stay here forever or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But once I saw them, I knew deep\Nin my heart what I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that, as a man, I must\Nset out to the vast ocean. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm leaving this place behind!\N--[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT] Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave for one reason! When\Nthe great pirate flag beckons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you must heed its call!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NCaptain! Say it isn't so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying again, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a bit hasty?!\NThere's no reason to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you loved\Nthis village!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's gonna happen to the\NUsopp Pirates without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] You've been\Nso good to me, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to leave without\Ntelling the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Captain!\NJust stay here! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp Pirates. Do you\Nremember this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we first met,\Nand formed the Usopp Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NHey, it's that liar guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh? Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you so\Nbuddy-buddy with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh! You're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're a really\Nfamous guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I know, you've\Ncome face to face
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with the man that is known the\Nworld over as Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually everyone in the village\Ncalls you Liar Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay! From this day forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're officially members\Nof the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Man up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers] A lot's\Nhappened since then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOG barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NA Cerberus! Scare it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon! Capture it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Flour Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NYou're amazing, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--[USOPP laughs]\N--[CHILDREN sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] But of course! I'm\Na brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk about the\Nold days! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper's right! It's\Nmuch too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of lie isn't like\Nyou, Captain! It's not fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that\Nyou're going to leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NYou're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] You're being stupid,\NCaptain! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHILDREN cry]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, men! Tell me\Nwhat all your ambitions are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up my dream\Nis... to run a pub!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life I've wanted\Nto be a master carpenter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to\Nbecome a writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, swear to me\Nnow that each of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,will continue on your paths!\NPromise me that you will never
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,let the fires of your\Nambitions die out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAs of today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our group...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the Usopp Pirates... [cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\N... are disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've eaten, we\Nshould probably get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NHere you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right\Nbeing out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think now I can truly\Nstart recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, my sickness this\Nlast year was caused
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,by the mental shock of\Nlosing both my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Usopp's friendship\Nhelped me start getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in bed\Nforever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all done\Nso much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a present for you\Nfrom the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to show you how grateful I am\Nfor everything you've done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored if\Nyou'd accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] All packed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Guess it's farewell\Nto this house, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]\NI can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This stupid backpack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Oh!\N--A real caravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Are you actually\Ngiving this to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] Mm-hm. As a token\Nof my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NIt's a slightly older model,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I personally designed\Nit and she sails like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a carvel-make\Ncaravel with lateen sails
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and a central stern rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a fine ship, and her\Nname is the Going Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] Allow me to\Nexplain the rigging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,First, about the Kruger\Nnet yard adjustment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it may seem a little---
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! You'd be better off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just explaining the\Ntechnical stuff to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] What a cool ship!\NHave you guys seen the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've loaded it with\Nall the provisions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you might need on a long voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Thanks! It leaves\Nnothing to beat tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "leaves nothing\Nto be desired", idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NUh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NSomebody stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's he doing?\NLooks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd better stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That weirdo, is on a collision\Ncourse with our boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hey, thanks guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NYou're really doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna take\Nto the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to get going before\NI have time to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPlease, don't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] I won't. I know\Nit's time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, don't be\Nsad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think, the next\Ntime I come back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about adventures\Nthat'll sound more like lies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,than my old lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] You guys take care!\NI hope we meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Well... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you antisocial\Nor something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking off for life\Non the high seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hope that we'll eventually\Nmeet again, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends. Right? So get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThis is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really a Pirate\NCaptain now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Don't be stupid,\NUsopp! I'm the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, NAMI, LUFFY laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NThere goes the Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] He fell in with\Nsome pretty awesome people,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not too worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NYeah, he'll be safe with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anybody\Nas strong as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always talked about\Nbecoming a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he's headed off\Nto live his dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the villagers\Nare gonna be sad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when we break the news to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Captain was the only person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who could liven things\Nup around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I just had a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION, CARROT]\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] They certainly\Nwere a pleasant bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NMerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NLying hurts... A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NAre you referring to Klahadore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be talking\Nabout Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really wanted him\Nto stay, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya. Years ago, one of\Nthe villagers told me a story
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about your good friend\NUsopp's childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a short time after his\Nfather left the village
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His mother, whom he was very\Nclose to, passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPirates! Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP panting]\NPirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's pirates are here\NMom! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Usopp, you mustn't\Nshout! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, we're saved! Dad\Nfinally came back for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. There you go with\Nyour wild imagination again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You silly boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. He always said\Nhe'd come back for us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and take us with him when you\Ngot better, didn't he Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father won't\Nbe coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm proud to have\Nmarried such a brave man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who dared to chase\Nhis dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about a\Nspecial medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff can cure\Nany sickness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So silly. You dream too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a dreamer! And I'm silly!\NIt's true. I'm proud of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the\Nson of a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you'll grow up\Nto be brave, like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NPerhaps out of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He continued to shout it after\Nhis mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hopes that one day\Nhis father's pirate ship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,would be at the shore, ready\Nto spirit him away to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and give him a family\Nthat he never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] The villagers say\Nthat his outlandish lies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,contain his most heartfelt wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPirates! Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] As someone else\Nwho lost both parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw you as a kindred spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and he couldn't sit by\Nand ignore your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for you too to\Nrise from the ashes of tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And live up to the example that\NUsopp worked so hard to set.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Cheers to a new\Nship and a new crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing, cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] They said that they\Nwere fighting to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp's wild stories\Nand outlandish lies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,always spoke of the\Njoy of being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They helped me through\Nmy grief by cheering me up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and telling me to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NIndeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna follow in our\Ngreat Captain's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NOne, two, three, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL inahle]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NPirates! Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates! Run for you lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] My life starts now,\NMerry. I'm going to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] That's wonderful,\NMiss Kaya. Just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Hey! This island gives\Nme the creeps! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.37,0:24:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Treasure hunting, huh?\NThat sounds exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Watch out!\NThere's something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.37,0:24:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] What's with this guy?!\NLooks shady to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] He says he's the\Nprotective god of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.63,0:24:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNeat! A scrub brush!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.79,0:24:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're the weird creature!\NGaimon and his strange friends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.30,0:24:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

